<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <title>Reset Password</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f6f9;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header {
      background: #2563eb; /* blue */
      color: #ffffff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #444;
    }
    .code {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #f1f5f9;
      border: 2px dashed #2563eb;
      color: #2563eb;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: bold;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      background: #f9fafb;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #777;
      padding: 15px;
    }

    /* ðŸŒ™ Dark Mode */
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      body {
        background-color: #121212;
        color: #e5e5e5;
      }
      .container {
        background: #1e1e1e;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
      }
      .header {
        background: #1d4ed8; /* deeper blue */
      }
      .content {
        color: #ddd;
      }
      .code {
        background: #111827;
        border: 2px dashed #3b82f6;
        color: #3b82f6;
      }
      .footer {
        background: #181818;
        color: #999;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      Password Reset Request
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello,</p>
      <p>You requested to reset your password.</p>
      <p>Use the following code to reset your password:</p>

      <div style="display:inline-block; background:#f1f5f9; border:2px dashed #2563eb; 
            color:#2563eb; font-size:22px; font-weight:bold; 
            padding:12px 20px; border-radius:6px; margin:20px 0;">
  <%= resetCode %>
</div>


      <p>This code will expire in <strong>5 minutes</strong>.</p>

      <p>If you did not request this, please ignore this email. 
Your account is still secure and no changes have been made.</p>

    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Inzozi School Platform. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
